name: Katherine Go
about: Hi, I’m Katie! I love creating products at the intersection of technology, entrepreneurship, and design to uplift communities I'm part of. On campus I’m involved with Cornell Creatives, Forté, and Cru. I make YouTube videos every week on my channel, alohakatiex, and I also co-host a podcast called The Secret Syllabus. I'm probably eating kimbap right now.
